 />\n遮打集合<br />\n(歡迎遲到，好過無到) <br />\n<br />\n2:00pm<br />\n<ins>美國駐港澳總領事館</ins> <br />\n為《香港人權及民主法案》請願</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽熟首歌未？<br />\n到時一齊唱 ：</span></span><br />\n<br />\nOh, say can you see,<br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed,<br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWK%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=4c87431c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">揮國旗(<span style=\"color: blue;\">美國</span>x<span style=\"color: red;\">香港</span>) ：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CAXjTX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CAXjTX.jpg&h=00eeedf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，九月八日見</span>"},{"pid":"8a5c906b656e75d30f410bf8dac1183df33fb9f6","tid":1544082,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:17:46.000Z","msg":"五毛post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c22c8055b04ac47029cc6eefe0dbe491a6fc096","tid":1544082,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:24:38.000Z","msg":"睇完comment唔怪得我d台灣fd成日屌柒台灣好多低能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話香港情況出現係台灣直接上香"},{"pid":"56fcf9bdabb5dab991508e6762970fbb7ee38c0a","tid":1544082,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:29:39.000Z","msg":"都啱嘅，但係你地咪一樣選過馬英九，軍事威嚇唔得，一樣有經濟拉攏，公產黨差啲有效靠拉攏台商而成功<br />\n<br />\n台灣人恨嘅香港人，同樣係望住香港回歸唔反抗嗰班人，我地一樣討厭呢班仆街，將上一代嘅錯誤怪落宜家班後生仔身上好唔公道"}]}